content:
@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #83541 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?

The regression issue template had a bug that meant the regression-untriaged label was not added. I opened a PR to fix the bug (#84713) and I applied regression-untriaged to issues that should have had it. This is one of those issues.
